Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该让自己变大变壮了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's time to grow myself large and wide
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.90,0:01:32.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:32.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.73,0:01:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,近来如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.73,0:01:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别靠太近  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.65,0:01:34.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not too close, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一举重就会发臭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tend to get smelly when I'm pumping iron
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check it out
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you're smelly
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都要归功于
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All thanks to
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先进举重设备
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my state-of-the-art weight set
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.16,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(857.192,160)}微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我无意让你失望  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:48.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to disappoint you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可拿这些来举重不会有进步的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but you won't see any progress lifting those
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  如果想要这样的胳膊的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:54.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is, if you want arms like these
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or these
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or these
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那看来我需要有人来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe I could use a little help
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果你想要我这样的胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:08.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, if you want arms like mine
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要参加我的训练课程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you just got to follow my training program
Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:11.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那可太棒了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'd be great, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都能看到我未来的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can see me now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,晚安  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good night, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶  那样的话就啥都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that would change everything
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早上五点来我家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:30.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be at my place at 5:00 am
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴个水头盔来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you'll need a water helmet
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才俯卧撑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only pushups
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加油  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:41.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.27,0:02:48.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:48.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, put them up
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感受到热量燃烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:12.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Feeling the burn?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:15.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm feeling something
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你已经热完身了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now that we've got you warmed up
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该来压压手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's time for the arm cruncher
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,压手  不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Arm cruncher, great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这只松鼠想杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This squirrel's trying to kill me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太好了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's great, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我玩得好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I sure had fun
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,改天再来健身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll have to do it again sometime--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这健身根本没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:43.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This working out thing isn't working out
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wimpy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是只花生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"I'm a little peanut worm"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是废到健不了身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.13,0:03:56.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you too much of a wimp to work out?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是不是像海绵一样弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you a weakling built like a sponge?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, now
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也能够拥有肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:02.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, too, can have muscles
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快用船锚胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With anchor arms
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以直接套胳膊上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:06.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They slip on like a glove
Dialogue: 1,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,充气即可使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just add air
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要多大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How big do you want them?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正常大小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,青筋暴起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Veiny?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想要泡妞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And for the ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长毛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hairy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买船锚胳膊以前我还是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was a wimp before anchor arms
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我是健美好手  人人都爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I'm a jerk, and everybody loves me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,立刻下单吧  废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So order now, wimp
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想跟他一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want to be just like him
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我一定要去打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I've got to get to a phone
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:39.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:41.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好啊  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mother-of-pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(538.749,530)}关
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.31,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468.652,622)}贻贝海滩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:51.31,注释,,0,0,0,,[ mussel（贻贝）与muscle（肌肉）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们以为是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:11.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who are you expecting?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蒂姆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tiny Tim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.41,注释,,0,0,0,,[ Tiny Tim：S01E01插曲"Livin' in the Sunlight,\NLovin' in the Moonlight"演唱者 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:14.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真是大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Big, aren't they?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄  你身材真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dude, you're ripped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:22.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(442.616,448)}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:22.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(983.368,426)}你
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在健身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been working out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:27.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me a second
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想去果汁摊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anyone for the juice bar?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:39.86,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702.978,412)}果汁摊
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你说  他好大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:38.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, he's huge
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们有在哪看到过海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:39.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you guys seen SpongeBob anywhere?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说大块头海绵宝宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:42.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean MuscleBob BuffPants?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:05:44.53,0:05:44.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.53,0:05:44.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我每天早上都吃二十个生鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:49.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I start off with 20 raw eggs every day
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but that's just me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.20,0:05:50.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:50.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,健身就是我的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Working out is my life
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还记得我从前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember when I used to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是那边那人的身材的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look like that guy over there
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:05:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.13,0:06:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也还记得我从前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I remember when I used to
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是你那样的身材的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,look like you, too
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可那已经过了好长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But that was a long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,饮料好了  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your drink, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.16,0:06:29.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:29.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄到这身肌肉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get those muscles?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己制定了一套健身计划
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've created my own workout routine
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后让我有了惊人的成效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's giving me amazing results--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉就从来没这么好过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have never felt better
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好家伙  你有什么诀窍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heck, what's your secret?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:39.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的健身秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your secret workout--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:41.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好高明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's smart
Dialogue: 1,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:47.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.26,0:06:51.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先我举起手  这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:51.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First I take my hand and I do this
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:55.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些肌肉说谎了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do these muscles lie?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真高兴能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你找到了适合你的健身计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've found an exercise program that works for you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你的健身计划
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, your workout routine
Dialogue: 1,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对我而言力度远远不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wasn't quite tough enough for me
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对这结果我无法反驳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't argue with those results
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在要做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.32,0:07:12.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What you need to do now
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是要测试一下你这身肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,is put those muscles to the test
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,贻贝海滩船锚投掷大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The big mussel beach anchor toss competition
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天举行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's today
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所有人都会到场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody will be there
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你饮料好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:20.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's your drink
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然你有这胳膊  你表现绝对不俗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:25.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With those arms, you'll do great
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太确定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not sure
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  去参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:28.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下   珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得这不太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:32.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's such a
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, wait
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:38.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is--
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,报名表
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sign-in list
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1071.49,350)}船锚投掷大赛\N此处报名
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:39.81,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1135.579,982)}投入口
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:44.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1053.465,302)}船锚投掷大赛\N参赛者姓名
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等珊迪  先别签
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Sandy, don't sign just yet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:55.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594.827,924)}投入口
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:57.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.80,0:08:09.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经帮你报完名了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I already signed your name in
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.84,0:08:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, great
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:16.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,话筒开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we on?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,酷乐湖第八届年度船锚投掷大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Goo Lagoon Eighth Annual Anchor Toss Competition
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了吗  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready, SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:35.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No problem
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能在上面加点芥末吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I get some mustard on that?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,首先上场的是  鲸鱼唐姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,First up, Dom the Whale
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,200码
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,200 yards
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看即时回放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see an instant replay
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来上场的是  龙虾拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up next, Larry the Lobster
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,210码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,210 yards
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪奇克斯上场了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here goes Sandy Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,510码
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:29.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,510 yards
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fabulous
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超越我的成绩吧  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Beat that, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来是  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:36.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Up next, SpongeBob SquarePants
