Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just kidding
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个海绵宝宝也太好笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That SpongeBob's funnier than ears on an acorn
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们都要发现我这都是假的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're all going to find out I'm a fake
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:08.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't give up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须拼一把
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to try
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.79,0:10:10.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can do it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有船锚胳膊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got anchor arms
Dialogue: 1,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm no wimp
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是健美好手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a jerk
