Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于帮你找到适合你的运动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think we finally found an exercise for you
