Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,十
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ten
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能帮我拿一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can you get that?
