Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有没有跟你说过你有多美吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have I told you how beautiful you are?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your tentacles
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:07.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your nose
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:09.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your eyes
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不太匀称
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:10.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little lopsided
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:13.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然我已经在蜡像中永垂不朽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.62,0:12:16.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now that I've been immortalized in wax
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就表示我击败了整个艺术传媒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have conquered all artistic media
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快啊  我宝贵样貌的映照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, my precious reflection
Dialogue: 1,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,笑一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:23.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Smile
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快前进  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hike, Patrick, hike
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你已经输三分了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You just lost three points
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.40,0:12:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.23,0:12:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five
Dialogue: 1,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,G7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:41.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-7
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,G7
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:42.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,G-7?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将军  将军
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King me, king me
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I lose
Dialogue: 1,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过今天不是星期二  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not Tuesday, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tartar sauce
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个无脊椎动物在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you invertebrates doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:57.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你知道现在几点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:01.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Patrick, do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知道  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是该找别的游戏玩的点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:07.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time to find some other game to play
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在要玩什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可以来回抛接这块贝壳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could toss that shell back and forth
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.19,0:13:24.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:24.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去捡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记住  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁捡到就归谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finders keepers
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.13,0:13:39.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:39.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There it is
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来捡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奖励分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bonus points
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.76,0:13:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥好像出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think something's wrong with Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好像失去意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:50.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He looks unconscious
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to do this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快下去  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off him, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在担心个什么劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他看着已经好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He looks better already
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可他摸着还是冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But he still feels cold
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就去把他放到暖点的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go put him in the warm
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得他会没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:20.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'll be okay?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可担心得太过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, you worry too much
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  有派大星在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Patrick is here and, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非常了解头部创伤  相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know a lot about head injuries, believe
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鞋子上的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that on your shoe?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看着有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It kind of looks like
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把他弄下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:42.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get him off me
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  这块要放这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:57.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, that part goes here
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哦对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:58.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, th-that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're almost there
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.42,0:15:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.42,0:15:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can do this
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is working
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is working
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's working
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, this isn't working
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不知道怎么说才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to say it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的朋友章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but our old pal Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.22,0:15:13.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:13.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:14.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:16.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he's pushing up daisies
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还以为他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:17.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought he was dead
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个是想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, are you two going to say something
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是要我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or do I have to
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不  别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, stay back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个有什么毛病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with you two?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别伤害我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:38.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt us
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是意外
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:40.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was an accident
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个到底在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们两个对我干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what you've done to me
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是让我逮到你们  我就
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.67,0:15:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I get my hands on you, I'll
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你了  章鱼哥鬼魂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, Mr. Squidward ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你不要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:55.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Spare us your ghostly anger
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  章鱼哥鬼魂先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Squidward's ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你不要缠我们的身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:00.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't haunt us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要什么我们就做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:02.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll do anything you want
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你饶过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just have mercy on us
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都听好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.07,0:16:11.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥鬼魂今天异常大方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's ghost is feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:11.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,unusually generous today
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他已经决定不让你们受苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:16.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He hath decided to spare ye a horrible fate
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.58,0:16:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们就只要顺从我的所有兴致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All ye must do is tend to my every whim
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,满足我的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.41,0:16:26.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tickle my fancy on demand
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是还要算上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does that include
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quiet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去照我吩咐的做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, do as you're told
Dialogue: 1,0:16:30.51,0:16:36.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,免得惹章鱼哥生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.51,0:16:36.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,lest ye incur the wrath of Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们好像特地弄了个美白霜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think they make a cream for that now
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这儿行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:43.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太热了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too hot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  太湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:50.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, too wet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:51.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.53,0:16:52.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Keep going
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.95,0:16:54.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太散漫了  罗特列克
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too loose, Lautrec
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.82,0:16:56.20,注释,,0,0,0,,[ 图卢兹·罗特列克（Toulouse-Lautrec）：法国画家\Ntoo loose（太散漫）与Toulouse（图卢兹）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.57,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(496.691,724)}鱼剧团
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:01.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too tired
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:06.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好想要东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,needy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奴隶们  给我拿点食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Slaves, fetcheth me some nourishment
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保证给最新鲜的  鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Only the freshest, o spooky one
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从藤上现摘的葡萄  鬼魂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:17.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A grape fresh from the vine, your ghostliness
Dialogue: 1,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,照你的意愿剥的香蕉  鬼魂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:23.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A banana peeled to your liking your incorporialness
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个西瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One watermelon
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,从施过粪肥的地里现摘的  鬼魂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh from the manure field your spookiness
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Art thou not pleased?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Enough of that
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在想吃点别的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want something else to eat now
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要非常难找的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something that's very difficult to find
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要吃什么  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you hunger for, master?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想要什么  我们就会去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want, we'll find it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们会去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:49.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll find it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,樱桃派
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cherry pie
Dialogue: 1,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你从哪弄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:53.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where'd you get that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就再去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, go find it again
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, get over here
Dialogue: 1,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,转身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now spin around
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:04.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's better
Dialogue: 1,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原地跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now jog in place
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说  侧腹牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Say "flank steak"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,侧腹牛排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flank steak
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像快要喜欢上这生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I'm beginning to like this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,停
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:13.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿这个用心给我吹首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now play me an elaborate song with this
Dialogue: 1,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这就只是张卫生纸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But this is just a piece of tissue paper
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,非得要自作主张是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always have to have it our way, don't we?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't do it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望你们今晚没什么安排
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:37.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I hope you don't have any plans tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.38,0:18:42.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为等我听到曲子之前你休想走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:39.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because you're not allowed to leave that spot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till I hear a song
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干活期间打瞌睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Napping on the job?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你应该要给我奏乐的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be making music for me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,作为这份无礼态度的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As punishment for this insolence
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥鬼魂命令你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:08.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward's ghost commandeth you
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去清理他的后室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to clean out his back room
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:11.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take that
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是  鬼魂大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:15.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, your ghostliness
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:16.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is fun
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you ready for this?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:22.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.72,0:19:23.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你来不来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, are you coming?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.51,0:19:26.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  要往这走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, it's this way
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:28.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.35,0:19:28.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:28.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.64,0:19:30.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要怎么把这团乱清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we going to clean up all this mess?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's easy
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把墙纸撕掉就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just tear this wallpaper off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看  你少撕了点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, you missed some
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是本漫画  看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.12,0:19:45.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a comic book, and look at this--
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是飞天魔鬼的起源
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the origin of the Flying Dutchman
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面说他死后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says when he died
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:52.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a1\pos(68.094,630)}飞天魔鬼的\N悲惨命运\N就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:52.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a3\pos(1261.754,300)}儿童世界\N促销
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,人们用他的遗体当橱窗展示架
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they used his body as a window display
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他不断出没于七大洋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.00,0:19:54.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now he haunts the seven seas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1197.666,414)}自此过后\N他永远出没于\N七大洋中
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就因为他永世不得安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because he was never put to rest
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不明白吗  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you get it, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要去购物了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to go shopping?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让可怜的章鱼哥安息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to put poor old Squidward to rest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:08.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Initiation
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是你仪式的第一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That was part one of your ceremony
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ceremony for what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要让你安息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're going to put you to rest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不想要安息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be put to rest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想要你们干完杂活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I want are those chores done
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们把后室清理干净了没
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, did you clean the back room yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:21.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.20,0:20:23.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我进去检查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go check
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, get in
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不进去那玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting in that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可你说我们可以让你安息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you said we could put you to rest
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可没说过那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything like that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快滚出我家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:35.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get out of my house
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.25,0:20:36.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:36.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:43.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我写了  这里埋葬着章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wrote "Here lies Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们可能不记得他  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You may not remember him, but"
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样够深了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this look deep enough?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, cut that out
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看  送葬队到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, the mourners have arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:57.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们得知你死之后  马上就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We all came as soon as we were sure you were dead
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你是想送我进疯人院吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.07,0:21:03.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, are you trying to put me in the nuthouse?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  只送进这个坑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, just into this hole
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我要向你坦白个事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I have a confession to make
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是个秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're bald?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是秃头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:15.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not bald
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm alive
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在快把墓碑拆了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, get rid of that tombstone
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,叫你朋友赶紧回去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and tell all your friends to go home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.30,0:21:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快叫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:22.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do it
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.13,0:21:22.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:22.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:28.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是你主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:30.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是你邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:31.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm your neighbor
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮个忙  别来帮个忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, do me a favor and stop doing me favors
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如你所愿  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,As you wish, master
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  他真的骗得我们团团转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:43.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, he really had us fooled
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对派大星  他才是被骗的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:45.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Patrick, he's the fool
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不承认自己是鬼魂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's a ghost in denial
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在最需要我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:49.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He needs us now more than ever
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're right
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他真的很需要上西天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:54.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He really needs to get up to the great beyond
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你再说一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:55.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, say that again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That again
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是另外那句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:21:57.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, the other thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是另外那句
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, the other thing
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是你之前说的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, what you said before when
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  是你之前说的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:01.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, what you said before when
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.75,0:22:02.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,算了  我有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:06.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never mind, I've got an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我够不到他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:11.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't reach him
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再用力吹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:13.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blow harder
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他飞升了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:19.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There he goes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he beautiful?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他到底要升到多高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How high's he going to go?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  他会一路升到西天去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the way, Patrick, up to the great beyond
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.57,0:22:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, friend
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,旅途愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:32.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy trails
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在到世界的另一边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:45.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's on the other side now
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.17,0:22:45.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:45.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.76,0:22:49.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他到更好的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:49.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in a better place
